description: AMUNDI JAPAN TOPIX UCITS ETF - DAILY HEDGED USD seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the TOPIX index, total gross return, whether the trend is rising of falling and has a monthly currency hedging in USD. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the most important stocks of the Japanese market. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi Japan Topix UCITS ETF - DAILY HEDGED USD (C)
